74
00:05:45,178 --> 00:05:47,847
-I shouldn't have fallen asleep.
-Did you drink?

75
00:05:48,890 --> 00:05:52,435
No, I didn't.
I caught someone last night...

76
00:05:52,518 --> 00:05:55,438
