79
00:06:00,026 --> 00:06:02,737
Over there.
I let her sleep in the night-duty room.

80
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:04,113
Who?

81
00:06:04,489 --> 00:06:05,990
I don't know who she is.

82
00:06:06,074 --> 00:06:07,742
